WEBVTT

00:33.640 --> 00:34.480
Wait.

00:36.720 --> 00:37.560
What is it?

00:38.200 --> 00:39.040
It stings a little.

00:42.280 --> 00:43.320
Bear with it.

00:53.120 --> 00:54.840
Didn't you say you were leaving?

00:55.720 --> 00:57.960
I've been getting things ready for you.

01:00.760 --> 01:02.760
Clothes. Shoes.

01:03.280 --> 01:04.360
Banknotes.

01:05.880 --> 01:08.120
Easier to carry on the road.

01:09.680 --> 01:10.640
And the divorce…

01:15.800 --> 01:17.160
The divorce letter.

01:18.680 --> 01:20.120
Just missing your thumbprint.

01:22.920 --> 01:24.040
How thoughtful.

01:29.360 --> 01:30.400
If you leave,

01:31.360 --> 01:33.720
there has to be some
proper closure between us.

01:34.720 --> 01:36.600
That way, whatever you do later,

01:36.680 --> 01:37.800
you won't be tied down.

01:40.320 --> 01:41.680
My affairs are none of your concern.

01:44.280 --> 01:45.240
What about you?

01:46.120 --> 01:47.400
What are you going to do?

01:49.680 --> 01:50.960
I told you before.

01:51.960 --> 01:53.480
If Lin'an stays peaceful,

01:54.320 --> 01:55.480
I'll build a pig pen.

01:56.120 --> 01:59.720
Raise pigs. Slaughter pigs. Sell pork.

02:03.000 --> 02:04.040
That's not what I meant.

02:06.080 --> 02:07.400
If I truly leave,

02:09.000 --> 02:12.000
will you marry someone?
Or take another husband?

02:17.960 --> 02:20.040
Marry or take a husband?

02:23.920 --> 02:25.160
That can wait.

02:25.680 --> 02:27.040
Life must go on either way.

02:37.920 --> 02:38.840
Very well.

02:42.800 --> 02:45.000
When you decide what sort
you prefer, tell me.

02:46.720 --> 02:48.840
I'll keep an eye out for you.

02:57.360 --> 02:59.600
Just not someone so cold and stubborn.

03:02.520 --> 03:03.880
With that sharp tongue of yours,

03:03.960 --> 03:06.680
you'd better worry about
whether anyone will want you.

03:11.960 --> 03:12.840
None of your concern.

03:13.680 --> 03:15.400
And if I do marry,
it won't be someone like you.

03:16.760 --> 03:20.520
At the very least, she'll be gentle,
virtuous, capable of running a household.

03:23.120 --> 03:24.200
Naturally.

03:24.280 --> 03:26.240
I've always preferred

03:26.320 --> 03:28.400
the refined type.
Well read. Smiles easily.

03:43.040 --> 03:46.760
We did go through hardship together.

03:49.320 --> 03:51.440
At least wish me a refined gentleman.

03:58.200 --> 03:59.040
Fine.

04:00.240 --> 04:01.840
Then may you have your wish.

04:06.560 --> 04:07.600
I'm going.

04:24.880 --> 04:26.360
Have you lost your senses?

04:28.400 --> 04:29.520
Was it really that awful?

04:30.040 --> 04:32.640
You're leaving anyway,
so why cross the line now?

04:32.720 --> 04:34.000
Cross the line?

04:34.840 --> 04:36.240
If I truly meant to,

04:37.280 --> 04:38.240
I wouldn't have waited this long.

04:39.880 --> 04:41.800
You truly like those pretentious scholars?

04:42.560 --> 04:44.600
You truly want someone like Song Yan?

05:26.960 --> 05:27.800
Who do you think you are?

05:28.800 --> 05:31.080
You leave when you please.
You kiss when you feel like.

05:42.040 --> 05:43.120
Do it.

05:49.240 --> 05:51.080
You have terrible taste in men.

05:52.160 --> 05:53.760
You're better off coming with me

05:54.640 --> 05:55.760
than marrying a snake later.

06:10.280 --> 06:12.560
My taste is terrible.

06:13.760 --> 06:15.080
That's why I saved you.

06:17.240 --> 06:18.560
I have an enemy.

06:21.120 --> 06:22.440
Either he dies

06:23.360 --> 06:24.520
or I do.

06:37.920 --> 06:39.200
Give me one year.

06:40.880 --> 06:42.160
If I fail,

06:43.520 --> 06:44.720
someone will send word to you.

06:45.400 --> 06:46.680
-You may remarry then--
-Who do you think you are?

06:49.000 --> 06:51.800
You call Song Yan a snake.
And you're any better?

06:53.720 --> 06:55.480
You take liberties with me.

06:56.800 --> 06:58.280
You claim you care for me.

07:00.440 --> 07:02.000
And you expect me to wait?

07:05.080 --> 07:06.160
Who do you think you are?

07:51.240 --> 07:52.800
You saved me here.

07:54.480 --> 07:56.240
Now you abandon me here.

07:57.800 --> 08:01.360
I guess that's closure.

09:41.880 --> 09:46.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

11:39.080 --> 11:41.240
HAVE A FULL MEAL

11:55.200 --> 11:57.560
When he was here, he barely spoke.

12:00.280 --> 12:01.560
Why does it feel so quiet…

12:05.320 --> 12:06.680
now that he's gone?

12:48.520 --> 12:50.440
Happy birthday.

12:50.520 --> 12:52.000
May you live long and worry-free.

12:53.320 --> 12:55.160
Such simple words.

12:56.160 --> 12:57.520
Was he afraid I wouldn't
recognize the characters?

13:41.960 --> 13:43.160
How did you hurt your wrist?

13:43.760 --> 13:45.800
Yesterday, while hauling pigs,
the ox cart overturned.

13:46.400 --> 13:49.000
I used my hand to brace myself
and sprained it.

13:49.080 --> 13:51.320
Her wrist often hurts.

13:51.400 --> 13:53.000
Slaughtering pigs is very tiring.

13:55.400 --> 13:57.520
We men wear these wrist guards

13:57.600 --> 13:59.040
for heavy labor.

13:59.120 --> 14:00.800
They are not for young ladies.

14:01.320 --> 14:02.680
You won't find any.

15:47.560 --> 15:49.120
THE TERRITORIAL MAP OF DAYIN

15:57.400 --> 15:58.920
Xie Zheng is alive.

15:59.440 --> 16:00.440
Why won't he just die?

16:01.360 --> 16:02.760
He did this on purpose.

16:03.280 --> 16:05.320
He stood aside until the empire
descended into chaos,

16:05.840 --> 16:07.920
then emerged only to make a fool of me.

16:08.680 --> 16:10.120
Marquis Wu'an has long stayed hidden.

16:10.640 --> 16:12.400
There must be a deeper scheme behind it.

16:12.480 --> 16:15.480
The Xie Army and the Yanzhou troops
have never been easy to command.

16:16.000 --> 16:18.360
If you remain in the northwest now,

16:18.440 --> 16:19.960
you'll be on the chopping block.

16:20.560 --> 16:22.760
It would be wiser
to return to the capital first.

16:27.120 --> 16:28.160
Commander!

16:28.240 --> 16:30.080
You think I'm afraid of him?

16:30.680 --> 16:32.280
I'll stay right here.

16:32.800 --> 16:34.280
Let's see what he dares do to me!

16:35.280 --> 16:36.200
I'd never imply that.

16:38.640 --> 16:39.880
Young Lord.

16:39.960 --> 16:42.960
Young Lord, please
don't let pride guide you.

16:43.040 --> 16:46.720
This is not the moment
to confront Marquis Wu'an.

16:47.720 --> 16:50.280
We must first bring word of his survival

16:50.360 --> 16:51.560
back to the capital.

16:51.640 --> 16:55.400
Everything must serve
the Chancellor's greater design.

17:00.200 --> 17:01.320
If not for my father,

17:01.960 --> 17:04.200
I would never let Xie Zheng off so easily.

17:06.880 --> 17:08.680
Young Lord's filial devotion is exemplary.

17:09.280 --> 17:10.839
Young Lord's filial devotion is exemplary.

17:11.720 --> 17:14.640
YIN

17:15.560 --> 17:16.800
Your Majesty,

17:16.880 --> 17:20.440
today the court is filled with debate
over the unrest in the northwest.

17:21.240 --> 17:23.560
I dare not claim credit before the throne,

17:23.640 --> 17:26.359
but there is one matter I must raise.

17:28.079 --> 17:29.080
Grand Tutor, speak freely.

17:29.680 --> 17:33.400
For reasons unknown,
Commissioner Wei Xuan detained General He.

17:33.480 --> 17:36.400
It nearly provoked civil unrest
in Qingping County.

17:36.480 --> 17:37.760
May I ask

17:38.560 --> 17:41.840
whether Chancellor Wei
was aware of this matter?

17:42.880 --> 17:45.360
General He's situation

17:45.440 --> 17:47.880
concerns military affairs at the front.

17:48.640 --> 17:51.240
Wei Xuan's memorial

17:51.320 --> 17:52.840
has yet to arrive.

17:52.920 --> 17:54.920
Why is the Grand Tutor so eager

17:55.000 --> 17:55.960
to step forward?

17:56.040 --> 17:58.800
What exactly are you insinuating?

17:59.400 --> 18:01.320
Do you seek to make something
out of nothing?

18:01.840 --> 18:04.960
Or to cast blame where it does not belong?

18:05.720 --> 18:07.120
I would never dare.

18:07.640 --> 18:11.160
Chancellor Wei should not
make such accusations.

18:13.480 --> 18:17.800
Your Majesty, I have joyful news.

18:18.640 --> 18:19.760
Marquis Wu'an

18:20.360 --> 18:21.520
still lives.

18:23.160 --> 18:24.320
Marquis Wu'an is alive?

18:27.040 --> 18:30.360
GUARD YOUR THOUGHTS

18:30.440 --> 18:32.840
Chancellor Wei, congratulations.

18:35.280 --> 18:38.880
If the Marquis has truly survived,

18:39.440 --> 18:41.800
it will bolster morale

18:41.880 --> 18:45.600
and make the rebels think twice.

18:46.400 --> 18:47.440
Yes, yes.

18:48.800 --> 18:50.480
Congratulations indeed, Chancellor Wei.

18:50.560 --> 18:52.560
Your trusted general returns.

18:53.160 --> 18:55.160
A most fortunate occasion.

18:55.240 --> 18:56.360
Yes, yes.

19:01.560 --> 19:02.800
Esteemed ministers,

19:02.880 --> 19:07.040
this calls for celebration
throughout the realm for seven days…

19:08.520 --> 19:09.640
Five days?

19:11.240 --> 19:12.520
Three days may be best.

19:13.960 --> 19:14.960
Well…

19:15.480 --> 19:16.920
How many days should it be?

19:17.000 --> 19:18.680
I concur.

19:18.760 --> 19:21.680
We haven't even settled on a number.
What are you concurring with?

19:21.760 --> 19:22.800
Your Majesty,

19:22.880 --> 19:25.400
Marquis Wu'an is young.
His merits are modest.

19:25.480 --> 19:26.960
The realm need not be disturbed.

19:27.040 --> 19:27.920
This humble subject

19:28.560 --> 19:29.520
cannot accept such honor.

19:30.280 --> 19:31.280
Chancellor Wei,

19:31.880 --> 19:34.440
setting aside Marquis Wu'an's
distinguished service,

19:34.520 --> 19:36.360
young as he may be,

19:36.440 --> 19:38.280
he is His Majesty's marquis,

19:38.880 --> 19:41.160
not merely your nephew.

19:41.240 --> 19:43.920
Could it be that His Majesty's favor

19:44.560 --> 19:48.320
matters less than your modest refusal?

19:48.920 --> 19:50.080
If that is the case,

19:50.760 --> 19:51.600
very well.

19:52.320 --> 19:54.680
I shall accept on the Marquis's behalf.

19:55.520 --> 19:57.080
We thank Your Majesty for your grace.

20:01.520 --> 20:03.280
XIGU ALLEY

20:08.000 --> 20:09.520
No! Mother!

20:09.600 --> 20:10.640
My son!

20:12.160 --> 20:13.640
Don't take him!

20:17.000 --> 20:18.040
Move it.

20:19.280 --> 20:20.640
Go.

20:20.720 --> 20:21.640
Move.

20:26.880 --> 20:29.840
Be careful out there.
Don't try to be a hero on the battlefield.

20:30.520 --> 20:33.280
You're not young anymore.
Being afraid of dying isn't shameful.

20:34.520 --> 20:35.720
Don't worry.

20:35.800 --> 20:38.400
The God of War from Xigu Alley
doesn't fall that easily.

20:40.640 --> 20:41.840
Keep up.

20:42.360 --> 20:44.200
-Hurry up.
-Move.

20:44.280 --> 20:46.480
Changyu's been in a foul mood these days.

20:46.560 --> 20:47.640
I didn't tell her.

20:47.720 --> 20:50.160
She's not even home right now.

20:50.240 --> 20:52.200
I definitely didn't tell Changning.

20:59.560 --> 21:00.720
Better they don't know.

21:01.720 --> 21:02.920
Best they don't.

21:10.800 --> 21:13.800
When I earn some spoils at the front,

21:13.880 --> 21:15.920
I'll come back
and buy you a gold bracelet.

21:17.320 --> 21:18.400
I don't want gold.

21:19.280 --> 21:21.040
I want you alive.

21:21.120 --> 21:23.040
-We already lost our son.
-Move.

21:23.120 --> 21:25.600
You cannot be taken from me too.

21:25.680 --> 21:27.560
You come back safe. You hear me?

21:27.640 --> 21:29.440
-I will. I won't die so easily.
-Keep up!

21:30.600 --> 21:31.440
I'm going.

21:33.280 --> 21:34.640
I'm going.

21:34.720 --> 21:36.160
Come back safe.

21:38.880 --> 21:40.000
Yuanbao,

21:40.840 --> 21:42.720
what about my little sister?

21:42.800 --> 21:44.880
If I leave, who's going to look after her?

21:44.960 --> 21:46.000
Keep walking.

21:46.080 --> 21:49.320
Yuanbao, we're not really
being sent to die, are we?

21:50.000 --> 21:53.160
If I die, I'll never see my mother again.

21:53.240 --> 21:55.480
Take that back. Don't speak ill fortune.

21:55.560 --> 21:56.920
Foolish word, let it be unheard.

21:58.240 --> 22:01.160
-Go strong. Come back whole.
-Move.

22:01.240 --> 22:02.520
-Mrs. Zhao.
-Go.

22:02.600 --> 22:04.080
-Pass a message to Fan Changyu.
-Up.

22:04.160 --> 22:06.200
-Up.
-If she looks after our families,

22:06.280 --> 22:08.840
when we return,
we'll serve her to the end of our days.

22:08.920 --> 22:09.840
-I will.
-Move.

22:09.920 --> 22:10.960
We'll serve her forever.

22:11.040 --> 22:12.320
-I will tell her.
-Get up.

22:12.400 --> 22:14.560
Hurry up. Move.

22:14.640 --> 22:15.560
Keep up.

22:17.120 --> 22:18.120
Stop following.

22:21.280 --> 22:23.000
-What are you doing?
-Madam Song.

22:23.520 --> 22:25.240
-Madam Song, help me.
-Let go.

22:25.320 --> 22:26.360
-Madam Song.
-Let go.

22:26.440 --> 22:28.640
-Let go first.
-Madam Song!

22:28.720 --> 22:30.360
I'm begging you.

22:32.960 --> 22:34.280
Madam Song.

22:34.360 --> 22:36.360
Please go to the magistrate

22:36.440 --> 22:38.560
and plead for my eldest grandson,
Kang Dan.

22:39.840 --> 22:42.200
His father already died at the front.

22:42.280 --> 22:44.080
He's barely grown.

22:44.160 --> 22:45.120
You know,

22:45.640 --> 22:47.440
if something happens to him,

22:47.520 --> 22:49.720
how am I supposed to go on?

22:49.800 --> 22:50.800
I beg you.

22:50.880 --> 22:52.080
-Kang, get up.
-Madam Song.

22:52.160 --> 22:53.160
Please.

22:53.240 --> 22:54.880
Get up first. We'll talk.

22:56.920 --> 23:01.840
Kang, serving the court is a man's duty.

23:01.920 --> 23:05.320
Besides, everyone has their own fate.

23:06.680 --> 23:09.560
You should send him off proudly.

23:09.640 --> 23:11.200
Let him serve the state.

23:11.280 --> 23:13.120
That way, he won't shame the court.

23:14.880 --> 23:15.880
Song!

23:17.080 --> 23:19.640
Then why don't you send
Song Yan to the front?

23:19.720 --> 23:21.480
Why does he get to avoid conscription?

23:21.560 --> 23:23.320
You insolent woman.

23:23.400 --> 23:24.720
Listen carefully.

23:24.800 --> 23:26.200
My son is a scholar.

23:26.280 --> 23:30.360
And studying in the capital
is also service to the state.

23:30.440 --> 23:31.280
Do you understand?

23:33.200 --> 23:34.040
Bring it.

23:36.480 --> 23:37.360
Fine.

23:39.160 --> 23:42.280
For old times' sake,

23:42.960 --> 23:44.160
take this.

23:50.520 --> 23:52.400
Call it a token of my goodwill.

23:53.320 --> 23:54.640
-See yourself out.
-You…

23:56.280 --> 23:57.320
Go away.

24:19.480 --> 24:21.240
-Milady.
-Move.

24:21.320 --> 24:22.560
Stop following.

24:22.640 --> 24:24.400
-Go back.
-Don't take him!

24:29.640 --> 24:30.880
Changyu.

24:31.560 --> 24:34.120
Changyu, you're finally back.

24:34.880 --> 24:36.960
If only you'd come sooner,

24:37.040 --> 24:39.080
you could have seen Zhao one last--

24:39.160 --> 24:41.600
No. I take that back.
What nonsense am I saying?

24:41.680 --> 24:42.960
What happened?

24:43.040 --> 24:45.120
Jizhou started conscription.
They took Zhao.

24:45.200 --> 24:46.840
-They took him?
-Yes.

24:46.920 --> 24:49.200
Jin Yuanbao and his men
were all seized too.

24:50.960 --> 24:52.000
How could this happen?

24:52.720 --> 24:53.640
Anyone inside?

24:54.800 --> 24:56.360
-Anyone inside?
-Yes.

24:57.320 --> 24:58.320
Yes.

24:59.480 --> 25:01.400
-Which household is the Fan family?
-That's mine.

25:02.000 --> 25:02.880
Any grown men here?

25:02.960 --> 25:04.200
No.

25:04.280 --> 25:05.880
Her husband left town. He won't be back

25:05.960 --> 25:07.160
for at least a year.

25:08.480 --> 25:09.880
The same old excuse.

25:09.960 --> 25:10.800
-Search the place.
-Yes.

25:10.880 --> 25:11.800
-Move.
-Wait.

25:15.600 --> 25:16.960
This household was already inspected.

25:17.480 --> 25:19.600
Her husband must've been among the men

25:19.680 --> 25:21.320
taken on the road.

25:22.800 --> 25:24.840
My… My husband was taken?

25:24.920 --> 25:25.840
You're certain?

25:25.920 --> 25:28.920
Is your husband named Yan Zheng?

25:34.200 --> 25:35.080
Yes.

25:35.960 --> 25:37.600
Where is he now?

25:37.680 --> 25:38.880
Can I see him?

25:39.440 --> 25:42.160
He was seized outside town.
Wouldn't have had time to pack a thing.

25:42.240 --> 25:44.640
They've already marched
with the main force

25:44.720 --> 25:45.840
toward Lucheng.

25:45.920 --> 25:48.440
If you leave for them now,
I am not sure you'll catch up.

25:50.480 --> 25:51.320
Withdraw.

26:02.960 --> 26:04.960
Mrs. Zhao, I'm heading out.

26:05.040 --> 26:07.040
Changyu, where are you going?

26:11.960 --> 26:14.400
Yan Zheng. You'd better wait for me.

26:18.680 --> 26:21.920
LIN'AN

26:22.000 --> 26:23.000
Move.

26:33.160 --> 26:34.120
Yan Zheng!

26:35.280 --> 26:38.960
The gates are sealed. Only conscripts
may leave. No civilians out of Lin'an.

26:39.040 --> 26:41.840
-Sir, just a delivery. I'll be right back.
-Not allowed.

26:58.400 --> 26:59.720
I'm too late.

27:04.600 --> 27:07.280
Son, your father…

27:08.360 --> 27:10.320
My lord, take this coat.

27:11.240 --> 27:12.240
Take it.

27:14.000 --> 27:15.040
Mr. Zhao.

27:16.000 --> 27:16.960
Changyu.

27:20.800 --> 27:23.640
This old fool picked the wrong trade.

27:23.720 --> 27:25.640
Learned to treat animals when I was young.

27:25.720 --> 27:27.080
Now I work wood in my old age.

27:27.800 --> 27:28.960
The officer says

27:29.040 --> 27:31.480
when I reach camp,
I can serve as a horse doctor,

27:31.560 --> 27:32.560
forge iron,

27:33.200 --> 27:35.720
and even repair siege engines.

27:41.360 --> 27:42.280
Mr. Zhao.

27:43.360 --> 27:44.400
Take this horse.

27:47.000 --> 27:48.400
Where did you get a horse?

27:48.480 --> 27:50.440
Bought it off Blacksmith Chen.

27:50.960 --> 27:52.960
They say horses are prized in the army.

27:53.040 --> 27:55.280
If you bring it along,

27:55.360 --> 27:56.600
they'll treat you better.

27:58.240 --> 27:59.320
Fine horse.

27:59.840 --> 28:01.200
A very fine horse.

28:02.480 --> 28:04.360
-Move.
-I'm going, Changyu.

28:05.200 --> 28:06.040
Move along.

28:08.240 --> 28:11.000
Mr. Zhao, this bundle is for Yan Zheng.

28:11.080 --> 28:12.120
-I couldn't find him.
-Go.

28:12.200 --> 28:15.040
If you make it to Lucheng
and you see him, please give this to him.

28:15.120 --> 28:16.640
Don't worry, Changyu.

28:16.720 --> 28:19.920
As long as I'm still breathing,
I'll see it delivered.

28:20.760 --> 28:22.960
-Take care of yourself.
-I will.

28:25.240 --> 28:28.040
-Take care!
-I'm going!

28:41.280 --> 28:44.200
WEI'S RESIDENCE

28:48.240 --> 28:52.360
HOLD FAST TO FIRST RESOLVE

28:58.720 --> 28:59.560
Father.

29:00.560 --> 29:01.880
Xie Zheng is still alive.

29:02.960 --> 29:05.800
I came back especially
to offer my congratulations.

29:11.960 --> 29:15.120
A border commander
repeatedly defies orders,

29:15.200 --> 29:18.400
forcibly drafts civilians, and launches
an unauthorized assault on Chongzhou.

29:19.080 --> 29:20.920
That is a grave crime.

29:21.920 --> 29:22.840
You should

29:23.360 --> 29:24.760
prepare yourself for punishment.

29:25.480 --> 29:26.760
I am not afraid of death.

29:27.560 --> 29:30.000
I rushed back only to inform you.

29:30.760 --> 29:32.320
Xie Zheng and He Jingyuan

29:32.400 --> 29:33.680
are in collusion.

29:34.880 --> 29:35.840
Collusion?

29:38.280 --> 29:41.480
One is my nephew.
The other serves under my command.

29:41.560 --> 29:42.480
How is that collusion?

29:43.720 --> 29:44.720
You are simply afraid

29:44.800 --> 29:46.920
that once Xie Zheng returns to Yanzhou,

29:47.000 --> 29:49.720
he will repay you
for that arrow you loosed at him.

29:50.440 --> 29:52.400
That is why you fled back here.

29:56.400 --> 29:59.480
Even now, you still shield
that traitorous ingrate.

30:00.520 --> 30:02.360
I only regret that arrow
failed to kill him.

30:02.880 --> 30:06.080
I merely did what you wanted
but lacked the resolve to do.

30:08.120 --> 30:09.920
If one day he truly kills me,

30:11.040 --> 30:12.280
would that make you happy?

30:15.240 --> 30:16.480
Insolence.

30:16.560 --> 30:18.960
Speaking to the Chancellor like this
is a grave offense.

30:22.960 --> 30:24.000
The Chancellor.

30:27.920 --> 30:29.320
He is your husband.

30:29.960 --> 30:32.000
Yet you never call him that.

30:32.920 --> 30:34.400
Had you grown distant, I'd understand.

30:34.920 --> 30:36.720
But you revere your husband above all,

30:36.800 --> 30:40.160
treat Xie Zheng as your own son,
and let Father treat me as nothing.

30:40.240 --> 30:41.920
Why is that?

30:44.960 --> 30:46.680
Remember this well.

30:47.680 --> 30:48.880
Without the Chancellor,

30:49.760 --> 30:51.280
you would have nothing today.

30:57.680 --> 30:59.280
If I were Nezha,

31:00.680 --> 31:02.600
I'd returned my flesh to you
than owe you my life.

31:04.800 --> 31:05.800
Xuan.

31:21.680 --> 31:24.360
Xuan was disrespectful.
He spoke out of turn.

31:24.440 --> 31:26.840
I ask that the Chancellor
take care of his health

31:27.440 --> 31:31.360
and not trouble himself over this matter.

31:31.440 --> 31:32.440
It does not matter.

31:37.040 --> 31:38.840
Zheng is alive.

31:39.680 --> 31:41.040
Zheng lives?

31:42.320 --> 31:43.880
Zheng truly lives.

31:44.400 --> 31:45.760
Heaven has been kind.

31:46.360 --> 31:48.480
The Chancellor's fortune runs deep.

31:49.240 --> 31:50.800
At last, you have an heir.

31:57.480 --> 31:59.400
WEI'S RESIDENCE

31:59.480 --> 32:01.960
Chancellor, now that
Xie Zheng has survived,

32:02.040 --> 32:04.120
the situation in the northwest
may soon change.

32:04.200 --> 32:05.520
Please give your instructions.

32:06.120 --> 32:08.000
Go to the northwest immediately.

32:08.520 --> 32:11.760
Test his attitude.
See where Xie Zheng truly stands.

32:12.680 --> 32:14.080
As for He Jingyuan,

32:14.160 --> 32:16.440
he knew Xie Zheng lived,

32:17.120 --> 32:18.360
yet concealed it

32:18.440 --> 32:19.960
and joined forces with him.

32:20.040 --> 32:21.800
Find out what exactly he's plotting.

32:22.520 --> 32:23.560
Yes.

32:23.640 --> 32:25.720
Prince Changxin attempted
to use refugees to breach Jizhou.

32:25.800 --> 32:27.040
That plan failed.

32:27.120 --> 32:28.000
He will strike again.

32:28.080 --> 32:30.600
With He Jingyuan holding Lucheng,

32:31.680 --> 32:33.080
who will now

32:33.840 --> 32:35.320
oversee Jizhou's affairs?

32:36.040 --> 32:37.280
Li Huai'an, perhaps?

32:37.840 --> 32:40.480
If I am correct,

32:40.560 --> 32:44.560
He Jingyuan's memorial requesting orders
is already on its way here.

32:46.080 --> 32:49.200
Li Huai'an and He Jingyuan
are master and disciple.

32:49.280 --> 32:51.800
Could it be that Li Xing
laid out this arrangement

32:51.880 --> 32:52.720
17 years ago?

32:52.800 --> 32:55.680
Hardly. It is merely circumstance

32:55.760 --> 32:57.240
meeting opportunity.

32:57.320 --> 32:59.000
Back in the Eastern Palace,

32:59.680 --> 33:01.360
I and Grand Tutor Tao
handled civil affairs.

33:01.880 --> 33:05.720
In military matters, there were
Xie Linshan and General Meng.

33:05.800 --> 33:09.200
Li Xing was nothing more
than a court jester.

33:09.280 --> 33:11.920
Then could He Jingyuan truly betray you

33:12.960 --> 33:14.240
and side with the Li clan?

33:14.320 --> 33:15.280
Unlikely.

33:16.120 --> 33:18.800
He Jingyuan values loyalty above all else.

33:19.600 --> 33:22.040
The Lis will not find it easy
to lay their hands

33:22.560 --> 33:23.760
on Jizhou.

33:23.840 --> 33:25.440
Go to the northwest.

33:25.960 --> 33:27.520
Bring back clearer answers.

33:28.200 --> 33:29.040
Yes.

33:32.920 --> 33:34.680
Seventeen years.

33:35.880 --> 33:38.840
Has the moment of reckoning come again?

33:49.680 --> 33:52.120
‎XIE

33:52.200 --> 33:58.520
Marquis Wu'an! Marquis Wu'an!

33:58.600 --> 34:05.160
Marquis Wu'an! Marquis Wu'an!

34:05.240 --> 34:11.719
Marquis Wu'an! Marquis Wu'an!

34:11.800 --> 34:18.159
Marquis Wu'an! Marquis Wu'an!

34:18.239 --> 34:21.159
Marquis Wu'an! Marquis Wu'an!

34:29.639 --> 34:31.120
Marquis, that wound on your face…

34:31.199 --> 34:32.280
-Ask no more.
-Is that injury

34:32.360 --> 34:33.719
-Mrs. Fan's handiwork?
-Out.

34:34.679 --> 34:36.600
-All of you, outside.
-Yes, sir.

34:36.679 --> 34:38.400
-Did she turn you away? Tell me.
-You too.

34:39.320 --> 34:40.520
Me too?

34:40.600 --> 34:41.840
Xie Zheng, you…

34:41.920 --> 34:43.000
No. I'm staying.

34:46.360 --> 34:49.679
Marquis, word from the capital.
Wei Sheng is already on his way here.

34:53.239 --> 34:55.120
So he knows I'm alive.

34:56.800 --> 34:58.240
Sooner than I expected.

34:58.960 --> 35:01.200
Prince Changxin has withdrawn
from Chongzhou.

35:01.720 --> 35:04.040
His next target will be Lucheng.

35:05.160 --> 35:07.560
He Jingyuan is rallying reinforcements.

35:09.600 --> 35:10.960
Prince Changxin trusts

35:11.480 --> 35:12.720
the Sui brothers most.

35:13.240 --> 35:14.760
Sui Yuanhuai and Sui Yuanqing.

35:14.840 --> 35:17.320
If the Yanzhou army
moves to reinforce Lucheng,

35:18.440 --> 35:20.000
the choke point

35:21.800 --> 35:23.160
is Baxia.

35:25.480 --> 35:26.720
Baxia.

35:26.800 --> 35:28.560
So Mrs. Fan really did hit you.

35:29.520 --> 35:30.720
Ow, ow, that hurts…

35:33.280 --> 35:34.120
Careful.

35:44.520 --> 35:47.000
-Mrs. Zhao.
-Ms. Yu. Bao'er.

35:47.520 --> 35:49.840
I thought it was you. It really is.

35:49.920 --> 35:52.320
It's been a while. Come in.

35:53.000 --> 35:54.080
Thank you, Mrs. Zhao.

35:55.160 --> 35:57.440
I came to see Changyu. Is she home?

35:57.520 --> 36:00.680
She took Changning to visit
Jin Yuanbao's family.

36:00.760 --> 36:02.680
She brought them some grain.

36:02.760 --> 36:03.840
They'll be back soon.

36:04.720 --> 36:05.560
There she is.

36:06.920 --> 36:08.600
Qian. What brings you here?

36:08.680 --> 36:09.640
-Changning!
-Changyu.

36:09.720 --> 36:11.400
Come inside. It's freezing out here.

36:11.480 --> 36:13.160
Quick, come in.

36:13.240 --> 36:14.880
-Let's go.
-You two haven't seen each other in ages.

36:15.600 --> 36:16.440
Go on, play.

36:16.520 --> 36:18.280
-Come on.
-I won't go inside.

36:19.880 --> 36:21.040
I came to say goodbye.

36:21.800 --> 36:22.920
We're leaving.

36:25.000 --> 36:26.120
Why?

36:26.200 --> 36:28.040
Sit. Tell me properly.

36:29.480 --> 36:31.600
-Come here.
-Coming.

36:31.680 --> 36:34.040
-Here. Have some tea.
-Thanks, Mrs. Zhao.

36:37.200 --> 36:40.240
A few days ago, my housekeeper's body

36:40.320 --> 36:41.480
was found in the snow.

36:42.560 --> 36:44.040
I reported it to the authorities.

36:44.120 --> 36:46.480
They said it was likely bandits.

36:50.440 --> 36:51.960
Did you notice anything strange?

36:54.080 --> 36:55.120
I can't say for sure.

36:55.920 --> 36:58.640
But I haven't felt at ease since.

36:59.680 --> 37:01.440
Jizhou is in turmoil.

37:01.960 --> 37:03.560
No one knows if Lucheng will hold.

37:04.080 --> 37:06.640
Most of the merchants have already fled.

37:07.200 --> 37:08.480
I'm leaving for the south.

37:08.560 --> 37:11.760
The trunks are nearly packed.

37:11.840 --> 37:13.280
We leave tomorrow.

37:15.240 --> 37:17.560
I heard Yan Zheng was conscripted.

37:18.600 --> 37:20.960
Why not bring Ning and leave with us?

37:21.680 --> 37:22.560
I'll go first.

37:24.080 --> 37:25.080
I can climb too.

37:28.280 --> 37:30.920
Thank you for thinking of me.
But I can't go.

37:32.600 --> 37:34.880
Yan Zheng was taken to Lucheng.

37:35.840 --> 37:37.560
I have to stay and wait for him.

37:39.800 --> 37:42.200
Mrs. Zhao is waiting for her husband too.

37:43.480 --> 37:45.440
She only has me now.

37:45.520 --> 37:47.320
I can't leave her at a time like this.

37:51.720 --> 37:53.240
Take care of yourself.

37:54.000 --> 37:54.840
Safe travels.

38:02.680 --> 38:05.360
XIGU ALLEY

38:07.400 --> 38:09.280
-This is for you.
-She can't take it.

38:10.000 --> 38:10.960
It's too valuable.

38:12.440 --> 38:13.720
Let Ning keep it.

38:14.240 --> 38:15.840
This one's Bao'er's favorite.

38:16.360 --> 38:19.280
Who knows when we'll meet again.

38:28.960 --> 38:31.560
But I don't have anything to give you.

38:33.160 --> 38:34.040
I want that.

38:34.760 --> 38:38.680
Mr. Zhao made me this cricket
before he left.

38:38.760 --> 38:40.320
He's gone to war.

38:40.400 --> 38:42.960
No one will make me crickets anymore.

38:43.040 --> 38:44.720
Keep it safe.

38:45.240 --> 38:47.240
If one day you no longer want it,

38:47.320 --> 38:50.000
bring it back and trade for your pendant.

38:56.080 --> 38:57.120
I'll treasure it.

39:00.520 --> 39:01.640
I always carry this.

39:02.320 --> 39:03.400
Now it's yours.

39:05.120 --> 39:06.440
There's sleeping powder inside.

39:06.520 --> 39:08.600
If you're ever in danger,
throw it and run.

39:16.400 --> 39:17.840
We're leaving now.

39:19.400 --> 39:20.280
Take care.

39:21.640 --> 39:22.640
Bao'er, come.

39:37.960 --> 39:38.920
The falcon's gone.

39:40.000 --> 39:41.520
Zheng's gone.

39:42.320 --> 39:43.720
Mr. Zhao's gone.

39:44.400 --> 39:45.640
Bao'er's gone.

39:45.720 --> 39:47.240
I miss them.

39:47.320 --> 39:49.720
You still have me. And Mrs. Zhao.

39:50.680 --> 39:52.240
When the war is over,

39:52.320 --> 39:53.360
they'll all come back.

40:10.320 --> 40:12.520
Master, a messenger from Prince Changxin.

40:14.280 --> 40:15.400
An urgent letter from him.

40:32.080 --> 40:33.320
You've come far. Thank you.

40:34.640 --> 40:35.960
URGENT DISPATCH

40:39.160 --> 40:41.840
Your brilliant scheme resulted
in Jizhou's grain being seized,

40:41.920 --> 40:43.320
for nothing.

40:43.400 --> 40:44.880
With Lucheng on the brink of battle,

40:44.960 --> 40:46.440
return at once.

40:49.560 --> 40:51.440
The Prince is in a rage.

40:51.520 --> 40:54.640
You should depart immediately

40:54.720 --> 40:56.920
and head to Lucheng.

41:03.320 --> 41:04.520
Naturally.

41:06.320 --> 41:08.320
Has the heir been located?

41:09.600 --> 41:10.600
Not yet.

41:12.160 --> 41:13.200
I take my leave.

41:42.200 --> 41:45.480
Master, that was
Prince Changxin's trusted man.

41:45.560 --> 41:46.840
How do we explain this?

41:47.520 --> 41:49.160
He was never here.

41:49.240 --> 41:50.440
What is there to explain?

41:51.720 --> 41:53.680
Prepare the carriage. We leave tomorrow.

41:54.200 --> 41:55.360
For Lucheng?

41:58.120 --> 41:59.360
No. We're going to find her.

41:59.880 --> 42:01.200
And that little bastard.

42:01.960 --> 42:05.800
Run! Bandits! Help!

42:10.160 --> 42:11.360
This way.

42:33.240 --> 42:34.280
And you are?

45:12.600 --> 45:15.760
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

45:15.840 --> 45:16.720
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
